Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero) Open Jobs 2014
the presence of a train in Indonesia is characterized by the first pencangkulan KA road construction in the village of Kemijen, Friday 17 June 1864 by Governor General of Dutch East Indies, Netherlands, Mr. L.A.J van den Beele Sloet Baron. The construction was initiated by Naamlooze Venootschap Spoorweg Nederlandsch Indische Maatschappij (NV. In DUTCH) led by IR. j. p. de Bordes from Kemijen towards the village of Responsibility (26 Km) with the gauge 1435 mm. this road was opened to the public on Saturday, August 10, 1867. is the major operator of public railways in Indonesia. It is completely owned by the government (BUMN) and pays track access charges to the government. One of its subsidiaries, PT KAI Commuter Jabodetabek, is operating electrified commuter service in Jakarta metropolitan area from August 14, 2008.
Requirements :A Citizen Of Indonesia;
Age:
i). undergraduate Level as high as possible 35-year per 30 April 2014
ii). Level Diploma (D3) extended our 30 years per 30 April 2014
Have an undergraduate degree and Diploma III (D3), with accreditation:
i). undergraduate Level: from PTN/PTS accredited "A" at the time of graduation date
ii). Level Diploma (D3): from PTS accredited "A" and "B" accredited UNIVERSITIES upon graduation date
A minimum GPA of 2.95
The man, a minimum height of 160 cm.
There is no bond work directly with other agencies including the TRAIN INDONESIA with PT (PERSERO).
Being of good character as evidenced by a letter from the NATIONAL POLICE (SKCK).
Healthy physical and spiritual as well as not color blind.
Never involved drugs and/or psychotropic substances.
Not bertindik and tattooed.
Willing to put in the whole working area of the company
If you are interested with this info please follow these steps: PT Kereta Api Indonesia (Persero)
Should you interested, please apply at the Open Kereta Api Hrd Recruiments
